      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASCEND JACARANDA (5) was below best last time when fifth but prior to that was a Grade 5 winner in quick time at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Likely to improve sharply this time. MY THREE BOYS (1) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd in a Grade 4/5 on May 20 over 457m at this track behind Slick Chance beaten 1.75 lengths (26.04). Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Hard to beat again. ALLERGY FREE (4) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 3 lengths away in second (20.00) at Goulburn in a Grade 5 over 350m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Leading player again. MAGGIE'S ETHICS (2) is new to this course but can play a major role.",
